(24, 'System Engineer', '<p>Responsibilities:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Perform full System Development Lifecycle </li>\r\n<li>Perform feasibility study, evaluation and analyze user requirements and propose solution.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare and maintain system related documentation (eg. job flow, functional specification, user manual etc)&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>Perform coding, unit test and implementation to live environment</li>\r\n<li>Provide user support and training </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Requirements:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Candidates must possess at least a Degree / Diploma in Computer Science or equivalent.</li>\r\n<li>Required skill (s) : Visual Basic 6, Ms Access, Oracle</li>\r\n<li>Candidate who has experience on Lotus Notes, RPG or Java development skill will be added advantages.</li>\r\n<li>Possess good communication skills and good interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>A team player with excellent analytical and problem solving skills.</li>\r\n<li>Able to work independently, present personality, self motivated and proactive.</li>\r\n<li>Fresh graduates with good programming skill are encourage to apply.</li>\r\n</ol>', 22, 4, '2400', 1, 2, 0, '2012-07-05 12:17:23', '2012-07-11 05:40:44', NULL, '2012-08-10 13:40:44', 14, 5),
