(76, 'BP HEALTHCARE GROUP', 'BP Healthcare Group has undergone aggressive expansion and transformation since its establishment in 1982. \r\nOver 30 years since its inception the group has grown from strength to strength alongside and in tandem with the nation''s rapid growth. The group has remained relentless in its pursuit of healthcare services of the highest quality for its customers. To this end the group continues to strive towards innovative technological advancement in the medical and clinical arena made possible through a concerted and continuous commitment in investing on ICT, state-of-the art medical devices and equipments and improving manpower training. ', 29, '275 Jalan Raja Permaisuri Bainun (formerly Jalan Kampar), 30250 Ipoh, Perak, Malaysia', '05-241 8484', 'services@bphealthcare.com', 'http://www.bphealthcare.com', 'default_employ.png', 0, 3227),
