(92, 'DURA TECHNOLOGY SDN BHD', 'The company has patented a product known as DURA which is a construction material embraced total solution for most engineering aspects. In a better perception, DURA is a cement based material that exhibit unique characteristics judged by high durability, extremely high strength and ductility which makes it an excellent resistance against abrasion, blasting and impact loading which will eliminated the used of conventional steel reinforcing bars in its design. The company produces products such as pre-stress bridge girders, blast protection panel and many others vary from customers requirement.', 37, 'Lot 304993, Jalan Chepor 11/8 Pusat Seramik Fasa 2, Ulu Chepor Chemor 31200', '605 201 681', 'dura@dura.com.my', 'www.dura.com.my', 'default_employ.png', 0, 3298),
(93, 'ALGOMINDA SDN BHD', 'AlgoMinda Sdn Bhd, is a premier provider of Information Technology Solutions that specializes in tailoring its approach to the individual client needs. AlgoMinda Sdn Bhd provides Information Technology consulting, LAN/WAN networking, deployment, integration, migration and security services and solutions. The company also provides on-going system and network maintenance services. Successful client engagements range from multinationals and public institutions, to small and medium size businesses.\r\n\r\nIn short, AlgoMinda Sdn Bhd simply provides a Health Check, which is an audit of clients entire network infrastructure systems. This service implies to the implementation of vast number of heterogeneous components and systems into one integrated functional system with full technical support in the package.', 17, '12, Jalan Lau Ek Ching, 30300 IPOH', '016-5566928', 'Yplem1002@gmail.com', NULL, 'default_employ.png', 0, 3299),
(94, 'Optotronic Semiconductors Sdn Bhd', 'As a leading contract manufacturer offering critical end solutions, we produce voluminous LED assemblies and final products for our customers on a daily basis.\r\nAlthough we possess strong manufacturing bases, this is only a part of the Optotronic story. Our strength lies more in our capability to manufacture what our customers want and participating in joint development exercise whilst providing both upstream and downstream supporting solutions in the process.\r\nWe believe in providing complete business solutions. There are no standard parts for us. There are only business solutions waiting for us to discover.\r\nCS Opto provides International Class packaging and testing services for High Brightness LED assemblies and light modules.', 37, 'Lot 10563, Jalan Perusahaan 3, Kemunting Industrial Estate,  34600 Kamunting Perak.', '05-8914990', 'sales@optotronic.net', 'www.optotronic.net', 'default_employ.png', 0, 3300),
(95, 'SYARIKAT CAHAYA MUDA PERAK (OIL MILL) SDN. BHD.', 'Syarikat Cahaya Muda Perak (Oil Mill) Sdn Bhd engages in processing and manufacturing of palm oil products. The company is based in Tapah, Malaysia. Syarikat Cahaya Muda Perak (Oil Mill) Sdn Bhd operates as a subsidiary of Ngan & Ngan Holdings Sdn Bhd.', 37, 'Batu 3 Jalan Bidor Tapah,  35007 Malaysia', '60 5 401 11', 'cahaya994@gmail.com', NULL, 'default_employ.png', 0, 3301),
(96, 'Guan Chow Cycle Sdn Bhd', 'First founded in 1940, Guan Chow Cycle is now a leading bicycle distributors in Malaysia. We represent over fifteen cycling brands in Malaysia and the region. Other markets we support include Brunei, Indonesia, Singapore & Thailand.\r\nOur growth and success is a result of our commitment to provide the best technical and marketing support to our bicycle dealers and after sales support to the consumers. After-sales support forms and important aspect of our business. Apart from being a distributor, we also establish our own bicycle assemble factory. We have assembly all types of bicycles ranging of OEM brands and our own brands at the same time.\r\nIn the local cycling scene, we are actively involved in sponsorships of national teams and major cycling events. This is our way of supporting the sport and giving back to the local cycling community.', 37, 'No.13, Hala Perusahaan Menglembu 5, Menglembu Industrial Estate, 31450 Ipoh, Perak, Malaysia', '05-2883957 ', 'guanchow@pd.jaring.my', 'http://www.gccycle.com', 'July-9-2012-3-34-pm-logo.png', 0, 3403),
(97, 'Ritz Garden Hotel', 'Business or leisure travellers will find Ritz Garden Hotel a perfect choice as we are strategically located in the heart of Ipoh city! Centralised between Old and New Town, we are easily accessible to most commercial addresses and tourist spots. Yet, the old charm of Ipoh beckons from the quaint Old Town where one can still find their favourite eateries and landmark Heritage buildings.', 31, 'No.86 & 88, Jalan Yang Kalsom, 30250 Ipoh, Perak Darul Ridzuan Malaysia', '05-2427777', 'sales@ritzgardenhotel.com / lily@ritzgardenhotel.c', 'http://www.ritzgardenhotel.com', 'July-9-2012-3-55-pm-logo-ritz-garden.gif', 0, 3404),
