(99, 'DNMC INTERNATIONAL SDN BHD', 'DNMC INTERNATIONAL Sdn Bhd is proud to be the Malaysian affiliate of Innovage International Inc., the fastest growing network of wholesale distributors worldwide.\r\n\r\nWhile INNOVAGE has grown in strength with over ten thousand offices in more than 100 countries since 1981, it is not until the early 1990s that saw our expansion taking growth in Asia, namely in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia, Brunei and the Philippines.\r\n\r\nFrom our single office right here in Kuala Lumpur back in 1993, we have grown into having 15 offices throughout Malaysia all strategically placed in major cities located from as far north as Butterworth right down to Johor Bahru in Peninsular Malaysia, and all the way to Kota Kinabalu in Sabah, East Malaysia.\r\n\r\nWe have also leveraged ourselves by having 5 key Divisions comprising of Merchandising & Flyers (DNMC INTERNATIONAL Sdn Bhd), Advertising and Applications (Pro Direct Sdn. Bhd.), Food Distribution (Save-On Foods Sdn.Bhd), and Retail (Ashten Products Sdn.Bhd).\r\n\r\nWe have firmly maintained our commitment to spread value-for-money products and services to the entire nation; even to the grassroots communities of Malaysia. Our reach throughout the country is both intense and ever-expanding.\r\n\r\nOur main strength lies in our motivated and vibrant distribution team and also our massive selection of attractive and desirable products and services.', 2, 'NO 10-1, PERSIARAN GREEN HILL, TOWN AREA 30450 IPOH, PERAK', '05-2493866', 'dnmcipoh@hotmail.com', 'http://www.dnmc.com.my', 'September-5-2012-9-46-am-DNMC_logo_320_240.jpg', 0, 3411),
(100, 'PANSAR COMPANY SDN BHD ', 'Business dealings in the region require a special expertise. It demands an understanding and sensitivity to local customs, traditions and trading patterns that only experience and intimate knowledge can bring.\r\n\r\nEstablished in 1961 with initial trading in hardware and building products, PANSAR Berhad has grown to become a major supplier and service provider of marine and industrial engineering products; construction and building materials; wood engineering equipment and supplies; electrical and office automation products and supplies; design, installation, commissioning and service maintenance of commercial and industrial air-conditioning and ventilation systems; and mechanical, electrical, construction and engineering works and services as well as industrial and marine engineering works and fire protection systems.\r\n\r\nPANSAR''s basic principles of growth are in our commitment to quality and in working closely with our partners and principals to provide customised price/performance products and assured professional services to our customers.\r\n\r\nAs one of the leading products and services companies in Malaysia,  it now has a network of 16 branches located in all the major cities and towns in Malaysia and Singapore.\r\n\r\nPANSAR represents a host of global and premium products that are worldwide leaders in their respective fields, supported by trained and specialised personnel.\r\n\r\nTo achieve its corporate goals and to face its future challenges, PANSAR is fully committed and dedicated towards its corporate vision and operational mission of\r\n\r\n"TOTAL QUALITY - our commitment to you."', 79, 'Wisma Pansar,\r\n23 - 27 Jalan Bengkel,\r\nP. O. Box 319,\r\n96000 Sibu.\r\nSarawak, Malaysia\r\n', '084-333 366', 'hr.admin@pansar.com.my', 'http://pansar.com.my', 'default_employ.png', 0, 3412),
(101, 'TAJ International College', 'TAJ International College is a higher education learning centre that provides quality education as well as professional/executive programmes. It is located in Ipoh, Perak, Malaysia. Since its establishment in 1996, TAJ International College has produced over 5,600 graduates. We also provide programmes that enable students to further their studies at university level. These programmes are designed to prepare and equip graduates with the right tools and knowledge to venture into the industries', 19, 'TAJ International College  100  102 Jalan Tun Abdul Razak,  30100 Ipoh, Perak Darul Ridzuan  MALAYSIA', ' (+605) 528', 'enquiry@taj.edu.my', 'http://www.taj.edu.my', 'default_employ.png', 0, 2881),
