(126, 'Impiana Hotel Ipoh', ' Welcome to the premier 4 star hotel in Ipoh (Formerly known as Casuarina Hotel Ipoh).\r\n\r\nWe are centrally located allowing easy accessibility to Ipoh Town and the Parkson Grand Mall. Also within 5mins of the Impiana Hotel is the Royal Perak Golf Club and the Sultan Abdul Aziz Recreation Park ( Also known as Polo Ground).\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe Impiana Hotel, Ipoh is ideal for both business and leisure travelers with a business club lounge, high speed connectivity, convenience store, boutique/souvenir shop, modern banquet facilities and great eateries to suit every occasion. Our Coffee House and banquet services are ''halal'' certified. The hotel offers 200 guestrooms from Deluxe, Club, Premier to Suite rooms with breathtaking views of the rugged limestone hills of Ipoh. All rooms are equipped with free WiFi, mini bar, coffee & tea making tray, modern bathrooms and telephone connectivity. At the Impiana Hotel, Ipoh you will find efficient international service combined with Ipoh''s hospitality at its warmest; just dial 1 and we are on call 24hours a day to meet your every need!\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe Impiana Hotel, Ipoh is the leading and preferred medium sized hotel amongst local residents, tourists and international corporate because of our commitment to high international standards of service throughout the hotel.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nImpiana Hotel, Ipoh is both peaceful during the day and with its live band performing at The Bistro, can become very lively at night! The hotel itself has an amazing history and The Impiana is here to continue that legacy by providing impeccable warm service whilst meeting your every need to make you feel right at home', 94, 'IMPIANA HOTEL IPOH 18, Jalan Raja Dr Nazrin Shah, 30250 Ipoh, Perak Darul Ridzuan, Malaysia', '05-255 5555', 'info.impianaipoh@impiana.com', 'ipohhotels.impiana.com.my', 'September-3-2012-11-06-am-IMPIANA-Corp-logo-IHI.png', 0, 4961),
