(178, 'Asia Printed Circuit Sdn Bhd', 'Since being established in 1994 APC has gained the reputation to be the most committed high quality printed circuit boards manufacturer in Malaysia for Prototypes and Small & Medium Production with fast and prompt delivery. We delivery in 24 hours, Fastest Prototyping service in Malaysia! We ship worldwide.\r\n\r\nWith APC, you enjoy greater mobility, productivity and flexibility. APC is a prominent printed circuit board in Malaysia due to our serious view toward quality. Through continually improvement of our ISO 9001:2008 quality management system, we are committed to provide high quality products and services to meet total customers'' satisfaction. We adopt IPC-A-600G Jul. 2004 Standards. Our PCBs and processes are certified by UL. Our products are listed under UL file No. E187419. In addition, our PCB comply to RoHS directives and Lead Free application. \r\n\r\nAPC values trust, honesty and integrity in our relationship with customers, suppliers and employees. We believe in good working ethnic and consistent quality performance. We respect long term relationship and intellectual property right. We believe profit and environmental balances should be of equal importance. We deliver to our commitment.\r\n\r\nAsia Printed Circuit Sdn. Bhd. is committed to provide world class quality printed circuit boards through continually improvement of Quality Management System and with prompt delivery, leading technology and competitive price to meet Total Customers'' Satisfaction and Regulatory Requirements. \r\n\r\nMeasurable Quality Objectives are established based on the framework highlighted in the above policy statement and reviewed periodically.\r\n \r\n 	 	 ', 20, '	203, Jalan Tembusu (Industrial Area),  	 	Taman Melayu Jaya,  	 	31900 Kampar, Perak. Malaysia.', '05-4665611 ', 'admin@asiapcb.com ', 'http://www.asiapcb.com', 'September-4-2012-10-53-am-asia_printed_circuit_1.jpg', 0, 5033),
(179, 'Survey Personel Service Sdn Bhd', 'SPS is a dynamic company with a mission to provide cost effective services to our clients, whilst sourcing suitable work for our consultants. Our approach of managing our consultants workload, whilst working with our clients on their forward human resources planning, results in our being able to provide a fast and reliable response to our clients requirements. Through our extensive worldwide network, we are able to source specialist services to meet most client requirements.\r\n\r\nSPS has experienced staff based at our Malaysia office to handle all our clients crewing requirements. Our staff are well versed in arranging Visas and making the most efficient travel arrangements, and so will save your staffs time in mobilizing and demobilizing our personnel.', 41, 'No.8A, Jalan 1/67B Off Jalan Mengkudu Ampang, 50450 Kuala Lumpur MALAYSIA ', '03 4256 188', 'sps@surveypersonnelservices.com ', 'www.surveypersonnelservices.com', 'September-4-2012-11-02-am-sps-logo.png', 0, 5034),
