(192, 'Imperial Garments Sdn Bhd ', 'Imperial Garments belongs to a Hong-Kong based group - The TAL Group of Companies. The TAL Group of Companies is headquartered in Hong Kong and is one of the largest garment manufacturers in the world serving high-end customers around the world. Our company has established a reputation for being an innovator in our industry with leading edge products and highly integrated supply chains with our customers. Imperial Garments is the largest garments manufacturing plant in Perak . A leader in the apparel making industry for more than two decades , currently Imperial Garments employs over 1,4000 people. ', 37, 'Lot 47 & 50, Tasek Avenue Tasek Industrial Estate Ipoh', '05-5466606', 'malaysia@talgroup.com', 'http://www.talgroup.com', 'September-4-2012-12-30-pm-talgroup.gif', 0, 5049),
(193, 'Overseas Express Container Lines Sdn Bhd', 'Overseas Express Container Lines is a leading International Freight Forwarding and NVOCC Operator Head Quartered in Malaysia and Having its own operations in Malaysia, Singapore , India and Indonesia.\r\n\r\nOECL with its Multiple Service Products has an edge in delivering what the customers need. It has carefully selected limited trade lanes and identified customers need to focus on those requirements and provide them service to their fullest satisfaction.\r\n\r\nThe Kind of commitment, competence, transparency in service makes the customer choose OECL for their Logistics and Supply Chain requirements.\r\n\r\nManagements Vision and Mission Statement:\r\n\r\nOur Vision\r\nOECL, will constantly provide customized logistics solutions to our clients in order to enhance their supply chain.\r\n\r\nOur Mission\r\nOECL, to be customers first choice for following services :\r\nNVOCC  FCL, Own Box Inventory\r\nNVOCC  LCL, Own Consolidation Services\r\nAirfreight services for import and export shipments\r\ne2e Supply chain services through an efficient global\r\nNetwork\r\nProjects & Break bulk services\r\nLiner agency services.\r\n\r\nOverseas Express Container Lines ''OECL'' was established in the year 2008 in Malaysia by a well experience team who have been providing world class logistics services for over 30 years in the various field of supply chain solutions.\r\n\r\nOECL''s Performance since 2008 has been remarkable in terms of handling multiple product efficiently with increased customer base, volume & revenue which has encouraged management to expand its own office network.\r\n\r\nWithin short span of time the company has firm plans to expand its own office network into other South East Asian countries.\r\n\r\nWith Vast experience in logistics industry the company is well placed to offer just what international market requires.\r\n\r\nThe company is dynamic and well tuned to identify the best for customer needs and provide the solution which is timely and effective ensuring customers satisfaction becoming the customers first choice.\r\n\r\nMultimodal experts assist customers in getting the best in whatever terms they require say cost effective or time bound deliveries or forwarding services.\r\n\r\nConsolidation of cargo on important trade lanes is one of company''s strength, fixed day sailings on weekly basis gives the edge for customer to prefer using our service, online tracking of shipments and e-updates for customers make them feel comfortable and updated.\r\n\r\nOECL would like to be a Vital Link to enhance customers Supply Chain Solutions.', 56, 'Overseas Express Container Lines Sdn Bhd Suite # 0909, Level 9 Centro 8, Jalan Batu Tiga Lama, 41300 Klang Selangor, Malaysia ', 'Tel : + 603', ' info@oeclines.com ', 'http://www.oeclines.com', 'September-4-2012-12-34-pm-oecl.jpg', 0, 5050),
(194, 'BZ ARCHITECT (IPOH OFFICE)', 'Architect firm seeking for Project and Design Architects with 3  5 years experience to join our creative studio in Ipoh, Perak.\r\n \r\nYou will need to demonstrate excellent organizational skills and experience delivering Excellent Design as well as possess excellent communication and technical skills. We would also expect you to have passion for detailing and construction.\r\n', 6, 'No.99, Jalan Chamberlain Hulu, Taman Chateau, 30250 Ipoh, Perak Darul Ridzuan', '05-2411828', 'admin@embz.com.my', '-', 'default_employ.png', 0, 5051),
(195, 'Al Rajhi Bank', 'FORWARD BANKING WITH A CONSCIENCE\r\nAt Al Rajhi Bank, we believe that the one thing that holds the world together as peoples of different nationalities, creeds and beliefs are values. Values define us, unite us, and garner trust from those we serve. Al Rajhi Bank is established on the bedrock values of truth, honour and respect.\r\n\r\nThese values we uphold continually, thriving as the universal bank for ALL peoples. These values helped us become a prominent banking force in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. And these values continue to drive us forward in our efforts to honour modern financial demands via the use of technology, and innovation of bespoke banking products.\r\n', 67, '-', '03 23017000', 'suhaila.osman@alrajhibank.com.my', 'http://www.alrajhibank.com.my/', 'September-4-2012-12-39-pm-download.jpg', 0, 2871),
