(202, 'Bromma (M) Sdn Bhd', 'Bromma is a multi-national company for manufacturing crane spreader. Spreader is a fully automated container lifting device which performs in the port during transportation of the container from the vessel to the port or vice versa. Bromma is the world leading company for crane spreader manufacturer and it is also known as the benchmark product for spreaders. Bromma (Malaysia) Sdn Bhd, located in Chemor, Perak has been in production since 1996 which had grown simultaneously.\r\n\r\nCultures and Values:\r\nValues Communication Listen well. It is the first step to responding quickly to customer needs. Innovation Every one of us must innovate  every department, every employee. It is an attitude of mind we all must embrace. Quality The symbol BROMMA must always stand for quality. Quality is something we must fight for, earn, through all the little decisions we make. BROMMA products, services, and business processes must reflect our quality commitment.', 37, 'Lot 19, Jalan Kelebang 1/6 Zon Perindustrian Bebas Kinta Chemor 31200', '0 5-29 388 ', 'malaysia@bromma.com', 'http://www.bromma.com', 'September-4-2012-1-46-pm-bromma.gif', 0, 5061);
