(204, 'DD Services  Sdn Bhd', ' We are a multi-national product development and manufacturing company,specialising in consumer goods which are exported throughout the world.\r\n \r\nOur IPOH office coordinates and administrates product development and order process management, working closely with our international clients.\r\n \r\nComprehensive networks of highly capable, thoroughly audited manufacturing facilities are available to manufacture consumer products. Acting always in client interests, we take responsibility to provide on-site quality control, in-house laboratory testing with efficient reporting systems to keep client constantly informed.', 37, ' 19 Medan Istana 2, Bandar Ipoh Raya 30000 Ipoh, Perak Darul Ridzuan', '05-2425 710', 'humanresource@emberton.com', 'www.emberton.com', 'default_employ.png', 0, 5064),
(205, 'Tokutomi Industries Sdn Bhd', 'Tokutomi Industries Sdn Bhd, a company established in 2005 with core strength in manufacturing Electro-mechanical products.\r\n\r\nWe are committed to providing quality add value and exceptional service.\r\nWith our vast manufacturing experience, innovative and creativeness, we aim to provide cost effective solutions to suit customer needs. We offer design guidance to reduce costs, improve yields and increase product reliability.\r\nOur services ranging from engineering development, design assembly, material sourcing and procurement, prototype build, product testing and high volume supply for complete systems build to final packaging and distribution.\r\n\r\nQuality is a way of life. All our products undergo strict towards quality and environmental management standards ISO 9001 & ISO 14001 compliances for excellence.\r\n\r\nWith our expertise and dedication, our goal is to become your reliable partner in assisting you to turn your concept become reality. ', 37, 'Plot No. 101666, Off Jalan Gopeng, Batu 4 1/2, Jalan Gopeng, 31300 Ipoh, Perak', '05 - 312 36', 'info@tokutomi.com.my ', 'http://www.tokutomi.com.my', 'default_employ.png', 0, 5065),
(206, 'Mesra.net Sdn. Bhd.', 'Each day, thousands of new websites appear on the Internet. Individuals and small businesses own a majority of these. Finding the right Web hosting company that offers a desirable package at an affordable price can be difficult and confusing. MesraHosting.net now offers a solution to this problem - the Malaysian Web hosting. We are able to offer you tremendous value to a majority of website owners. Our unique structure allows us to simplify our management and reduce overhead costs. These savings are then relayed directly to you, our customer. MesraHosting.net eliminates the unnecessary confusion of deciding a reliable Web hosting solution to meet all your personal and business needs.\r\n\r\nEstablished in 1996, Mesra.net Sdn. Bhd. (Previously Known As Multi System Resources And Network Sdn Bhd.) started a free web-based email service. Over the years it has developed into a directories and information website that provide many information and services to the users. We have now ventured into web hosting services, with the aim to provide a reliable service for our customers at a considerably reduced price, and competitive to what is already on offer in Malaysia. From our own experience of web services, we believe we could provide the same, if not better, standard of services. Already established at Subang Jaya, Selangor & Ipoh, Perak for the past few years, our data centre is only located at TMNet Netmyne, Cyberjaya, the capital of Information Technology of Malaysia.\r\n\r\nMany web companies subscribe to web hosting provider overseas, especially from the Unites States. Service is provided over long distance phone calls. We believe that web hosting could be provided better by a local company, and at a much reduced rate. Support can be provided 24 hours and does not cost any overseas call. Being a local company, we could provide services with a local provider and better understanding of your needs. ', 97, 'No. 5, Persiaran Putra 1, Jalan Taiping, 33000 Kuala Kangsar, Perak', '05-7733333', 'info@mesrahosting.net', 'http://www.mesrahosting.net', 'default_employ.png', 0, 5067),
