(212, 'Zenbes Sdn. Bhd.', 'ZeNBeS Sdn. Bhd.(hereafter named as ZeNBeS) a Bumi controlled organization, is subsidiary to Sri Communication Group of Companies, which was incorporated in 1991 to manufacture structural concrete masonry units and interlocking pavers to cater to the demands of the existing market for quality products.\r\n\r\nWith sophisticated technology support from Zenith GmbH, Germany, and Besser, USA, respectively who are world leaders in the manufacture of machinery for our products, we are able to achieve monthly production capacity of 50,000 m2 for pavers and 600,000 pieces of concrete hollow blocks respectively.\r\n\r\nOur existing products meet the relevant British Standard (BS) and Malaysia Standard (MS) requirements, inclusive of fire rating for the concrete masonry units. With emphasis on material and finished products quality, ZeNBeS has, over the years, not only obtaining market share in West & East Malaysia, but also made significant inroads into export of its products to Mauritius, Singapore and Fuji.\r\n\r\nZeNBeS, follows a proactive approach to management, continuously seeking at ways and ideas to enhance quality, working directly with end users to create flexible products suited to the exact requirements of our customers.\r\n\r\nTherefore, we are committed to continually maintaining and improving the quality of our products and services in order to achieve Total Customer Satisfaction. With full commitment from the top management and staff, the implementation of quality management system ISO 9001:2000 and conformance to BS & MS requirements, we will be able to achieve the product quality consistency through good work practice and at the same time gain the confidence of our customers.\r\n\r\nAt the end we assure you, the prospective user, of quality products at very competitive pricing. ', 1, '44, 1st Floor, Jln Tun Sambathan 3, Brickfields, 50470 Kuala Lumpur', '05-357 3628', 'info@zenbes.com.my', 'http://www.zenbes.com.my', 'September-4-2012-4-35-pm-PUZZLE-header.jpg', 0, 5075),
