(220, 'BP Healthcare Group', 'BP Healthcare Group was founded on 1st January,1982 by Dato Beh Chun Chuan and his wife Datin Poh Lay See.\r\n\r\nDato Beh Chun Chuan is the founder and Chairman of BP Healthcare Group of companies which includes BP Diagnostic Centre, BP Clinical Lab, BE-P Pharmacy, BP Business Solutions, Labpro, BP Food Testing, BP Ambulatory, BP Radiology and BP Properties.\r\n\r\nDato Beh is the pioneer shareholder and director of Hospital Pantai Ipoh and Sunway City (Ipoh) Sdn Bhd.\r\n\r\nSunway City (Ipoh) Sdn Bhd is an integrated multi-billion resort township in Ipoh. Dato Beh private investment, Shan San Ling Holding Sdn Bhd and his partners jointly owned Kinta Valley Resort Sdn Bhd investment which has equity in Sunway City (Ipoh) Sdn Bhd.\r\n\r\nDato Beh was a past committee member of Perak Chinese Maternity Hospital. He was also the founder and past President of Malaysian Association of Private Medical Laboratories.\r\n\r\nDatin Poh Lay See is a property investor and developer together with her family''s investment holdings. Datin Poh comes from a prominent business family in Ipoh, Perak. The Poh family''s initial core business in the early 50''s was in commodities trading, wholesales and retailing. Today their group diversified into many businesses.\r\n\r\nDatin Poh Lay See''s father Mr. Poh Chee Meng founded Aun Huat Brothers Group of companies together with his other business partners founded many big local and international corporations. Mr. Poh Chee Meng is the first founding pioneer member of IGB Corporation Bhd, Ipmuda Bhd, IGI (Singapore) Ltd, Ruberrex Bhd and many others.\r\n\r\nWe are a leading healthcare group with nationwide network of branches. Charting a new course into more dynamic future, we seek individuals to join our goals and objectives.\r\n\r\nSuccessful candidates can expect an attractive remuneration package as well as excellent opportunities for career and personal development. We also provide comprehensive and continuous training for staff.\r\n\r\nWe offer more than just a place to work. We continually strive to create an environment that encourages our Associates to grow.\r\n\r\nWelcome to the BP Careers site - here you''ll find information about career opportunities within each of the BP business entities. \r\n\r\nWe offer challenging opportunities to people looking to join an organization that recognizes and rewards individual contributors. Dynamic working environment, a wide range of career options and career advancement opportunities, plus the chance to join the leading healthcare group with nationwide network of branches', 29, 'The HR Department B.P. Healthcare Group Address : 275, Jalan Kampar, 30250 Ipoh, Perak.', '05-241 8484', 'services@bphealthcare.com / recruit@bphealthcare.c', 'http://www.bphealthcare.com', 'September-5-2012-10-04-am-bphealth.gif', 0, 5089),
(221, 'C.L.P Industries Sdn Bhd', 'The CLP group of companies is a well-established network across Asia, with our headquarters in Singapore. The CLP group is engaged in various businesses, including industrial solvents, speciality & intermediate chemicals, waste and cooling water treatment chemicals, leather chemicals, enzyme chemicals, construction chemicals, waterproofing & floor coating specialist works etc.\r\n\r\nFrom its humble beginnings as a sole proprietorship dealing in paints back in 1947, CLP has grown steadily over the years and expanded its businesses strategically across Asia. Today, the CLP group records turnover in excess of S$100 million. Beyond the financials, our wealth of knowledge and experience developed over the years enabled us to be optimistic of the future as the Asian markets continue to evolve.\r\n\r\nWe welcome you on this journey to find out more about our group and our commitment to providing quality products and services. We hope that you too, like many of our valued customers over the years, will find us to be a trusted business partner.', 12, '9A, Jalan Perindustrian Silibin 1 Kawasan Perindustrian Ringan Silibin Silibin 30100, Ipoh, Malaysia', '05-5292010', 'clp@clp.com.my', 'http://www.clp.com.sg', 'September-5-2012-10-16-am-logo.gif', 0, 5090),
(222, 'Imatera Digital Image Services Sdn Bhd ', 'Imatera Digital Image Services Sdn. Bhd. (IDIS) is an Information Technology Integrator company that specializes in delivering technology solutions to meet the needs of our clients. IDIS maintains a fundamental commitment to excellence that is evident in everything we do. Our commitment is to understand and meet the needs of both our clients and consultants by delivering quality, value-added solutions.\r\n\r\nWe deliver strategic business solutions utilizing the most robust and powerful information technology available today  with special emphasis on budget concerns and time constraints.\r\n\r\nWe offer a competitive advantage to our clients with speed-to market, adaptability and flexibility, efficiency and cost savings, expert knowledge and risk transfer.\r\n\r\nWe provide practical solutions that enhance the value of client investment resulting in better use of company information, improved service, increased productivity and reduced expense.\r\n\r\n \r\nIDIS is looking for you if you are looking for a challenging career that offers a fun, open, interactive, and team-oriented work environment. If you believe in working hard, playing hard, and thinking beyond the usual take a moment to browse our upcoming job opportunities.\r\n\r\nIDIS provides a wide range of Information Technology Solution to its commercial and government clients. Our business is our people and they are paramount to our success. Our experienced, highly-trained, focused team of professionals, is prepared to deliver solutions immediately in the following areas such as Project Management and Software & Application Development.\r\n\r\nIDIS was built on project management competency. Every client engagement, regardless of its market, is managed using a repeatable project management methodology. Our people work together like a fine-tuned machine; they have practical, proven, hands-on project management experience. With project management practices as the foundation of our team''s working philosophy, we deliver consistent, results-oriented, repeatable solutions to each and every client.\r\n\r\nWe clearly recognize that the client relationship and teaming effort is key to our success. This becomes a cornerstone in allowing our team to function at capacity and deliver solutions beyond conventional expectations. Our experience and expertise is substantial in the areas of program/project management, requirements analysis, network management, application development, system integration and training.\r\n\r\nIf you are looking for a work environment that is fun, open, interactive, and team-oriented, yet requires strong individual drive, we might be the right company for you. At IDIS, we believe in celebrating success, encouraging growth, and nurturing both teams and individuals. We work hard, play hard, think beyond the usual, and collaborate our efforts to ensure the best possible results.\r\n\r\nIDIS supports personal and career development through individual growth plans, training opportunities, regular performance feedback, and much more. With excellence as our primary objective, we encourage a work/life balance for all employees. We know that our people are our future.\r\n\r\nOur approach is to develop, deliver, and support integrated information technology solutions. We recognize the need for comprehensive, interactive and cost effective solutions that are customized to address client''s environment. Our clients commonly referred to us as their complete total solutions provider.We provide solutions that are designed for your business needs and your satisfaction is guaranteed.\r\n\r\n\r\nBusiness Focused\r\n\r\nAt IDIS we believe in the bottom line. Without a strategic plan, technology can be an expensive waste. When you work with us, we''ll keep the work focused on improving your business. We will help you streamline operations, provide better and faster solution.\r\n\r\nCustom Solutions\r\n\r\nWe offer consultation. We want to analyze your business and develop solutions that work for you.  Our team of expertises fill in the gaps left by software and hardware vendors through a broad knowledge of the latest technology and years of hands on experience with businesses like yours.\r\n\r\nSatisfied Customers\r\n\r\nWe strive to exceed our customers expectations in terms of project implementation as well as ongoing support.   Through the use of customer support best practices and dedicated engineers assigned to your business, IDIS ensures that a higher level of quality work is performed in timely manner.\r\n\r\nTechnical Expertise\r\n\r\nIDIS professionals have academic and practical experience in various technical fields such as Computer Science, Information Systems Management, Business Administration and Marketing.\r\n', 97, ' WISMA IMATERADIGITAL, No. 8, Jalan Jelatek Dua, Jelatek Business Park, 54200 Kuala Lumpur Malaysia', '03 - 4257 9', '	idis@imateradigital.com', '	 http://www.imateradigital.com / http://portal.im', 'September-5-2012-10-28-am-ima.png', 0, 5091),
(223, 'Farmcochem Sdn Bhd ', 'Established in 1984, Farmcochem is one of South East Asia''s most dynamic agribusiness companies providing crop proctection and plant nutrition solutions. We are one of the leading companies in the generic crop proctection industry in Malaysia and rapidly expanding our business across the region.\r\n\r\nIn line with our expansion plans in Malaysia, we are looking for outstanding individual to join our dynamic and rapidly growing company. Whether you are an experienced professional or taking that first step in your career, we offer you a unique opportunity to further your prospects and maximize your talent.', 4, ' A-05-07, Empire Office, Empire Subang, Jalan SS 16/1, SS 16, 47500 Subang Jaya, Selangor.', '03-5022 228', 'hr@farmcochem.com', '-', 'September-5-2012-10-33-am-farmcochem1a_02.jpg', 0, 5092),
(224, 'Envotech Network Sdn Bhd', 'The Company was established in 2006. The principal activity is in manufacturing of mechanical security seals and RFID E-seal. The Company is led by a group of professionals with combined experience of more than half a century, particularly in design and manufacture of security seals. In recent months, much research and development work has been undertaken to improve design and security to meet international standard and compliance.\r\nThe company is quickly becoming a premier player in the seal industry. Today, Envotech is making inroads in the supply of RFID E-seals and conventional mechanical seals to a wide range of industries around the world.\r\nEnvotech''s growth is spurred by innovative products development that meets and international recognized standard; this was achieved by forging partnerships with technology companies and IP licensing.\r\nThe Company''s manufacturing plant is located in Peninsular Malaysia. Strategic business operations and partners covering the United States, United kingdom, Switzerland, Singapore, China, Korea, and the Middle East.\r\nIn many other countries, strategic alliances are also forged with partners who are global players in their industries.\r\nThe Team''s decades of international exposure is the key to our successful penetration into the airline, intermodal shipping, banking, transportation, chemical, manufacturing, pharmaceutical and healthcare industries. While our RFID e-seal are employed in point to point custodial transportation with back-end visibility. They are currently deployed in United States, Thailand and China.', 103, 'No. 25, Jalan Kilang 2, Kawasan Perindustrian Jelapang  (Taman Pertama) 30100 Jelapang, Ipoh, Perak Malaysia / Envotech Sdn. Bhd.(754812-T) 36, Lorong IKS Juru 3, Taman IKS, 14100 Juru, Bukit Mertajam, Penang, Malaysia', '+ 605 527 8', 'info@envotech.com.my', 'http://www.envotech.com.my', 'September-5-2012-10-59-am-envotech.JPG', 0, 5093),
