(282, 'Airborne Informatics Sdn Bhd', 'Airborne Informatics Sdn Bhd, wholly owned by Wira Kerjaya Sdn Bhd, was formed to venture into the high technology areas. We began by enhancing our expertise in geospatial data acquisition and data management especially in airborne remote sensing and in customization of GIS for various clients. We have since secured major projects in Malaysia and the neighboring countries in our quest to be a world class technology solutions provider.\r\n\r\nAt Airborne Informatics, we apply some of worlds most modern techniques and solutions to adhere strictly to principles such as timely completion with the best quality standard by providing a professional and comprehensive solution in the survey and mapping need.\r\n\r\nAirborne Informatics always believed that high quality and accurate maps will produce accurate and comprehensive information to plan and execute the development of any country / project precisely and in most cost effective.\r\n\r\nAirborne Informatics is focused in spearheading modern and hi-tech solution in geospatial industry. Expertise involved including:\r\n\r\n     Airborne laser mapping and remote sensing,\r\n     Global Positioning System (GPS) and land surveying,\r\n     Bathymetric and oceanographic surveying,\r\n     Multispectral and hyperspectral imaging,\r\n     Design and implementation of Geographical Information System (GIS),\r\n     Detailed engineering (including by terrestrial laser pulse system),\r\n     Vehicular laser scanning system, and\r\n     Digital underground utilities mapping.', 16, '13E, 5th Floor, Block 2, Worldwide Business Park, Jalan Tinju 13/50, 40675 Shah Alam, Selangor', '03 - 5511 1', 'info@lidar.com.my', 'http://www.lidar.com.my', 'September-13-2012-10-16-am-airborne_logo.png', 0, 5249),
