(326, 'Beta Mutiara Corporation Berhad', 'Constructive ideas come from creative people working together as a team.  BETA is a company that builds off each others strengths and experience to achieve the results you want.\r\n\r\nSince 2000, BETA has been continually building up a reputation for quality, offering their clients skilled workmanship and impressive end-results. Their commitment to customer satisfaction starts by understanding your vision, turning it into blueprints and getting the job done the way you expect it.\r\n\r\nFrom management staff to job-site crews, BETA has a skilled and loyal workforce unique to the industry. BETA is managed by a board of directors, each member with over 20 years experience with the company. On the job, their dedicated crews of carpenters and various tradesmen bring experience and skills to every phase of the project.\r\n\r\nBreak ground on your next building project with BETA and rely on our proven team to give you the constructive ideas you expect. ', 15, 'No6,6A,6B & 6C\r\nPersiaran Greentown 4C\r\nGreentown Avenue\r\n30450 Ipoh\r\nPerak Darul Ridzuan', '05-2410366', 'www.bmtgroup.com.my', 'bmtgroup.com.my', 'October-10-2012-10-58-am-bmcb.png', 0, 5954),
