(328, 'SEEMSOON HOTEL SDN BHD', 'Seemsoon Hotel, A perfect choice of accommodation as it is strategically located in the heart of Ipoh city! This makes our hotel an ideal starting point to your business, city or leisure trip.\r\n\r\nFrom the hotel, you can proximately access to most of the local destination of interest. Just 5 minutes'' walk to many famous delicious local eateries and night entertainment, 10 minutes'' walk to Sri Maju Bus Terminal, 10 minutes'' drive to Ipoh Airport and local attractions such as Ipoh City Hall, Ipoh Railway Station, Sam Poh Tong, Perak Cave Temple and etc.\r\n\r\nSeemsoon Hotel, featuring 100 rooms spread out in a six storey building. Each guestroom is enhanced with stylish design where guests'' comfort is the utmost priority. Our rooms are fully equipped with modern appliances where you can enjoy your stay after a long day spent in working or exploring the city.\r\n\r\nEnjoy Seemsoon Hotel''s well kempt and peaceful environment. Warm and hospitable staff service and extensive modern room facilities will ensure you an impressive and memorable stay.', 31, 'NO 2, REGAT DATO MAHMUD, 31650 IPOH PERAK', '05-2556888', 'hr@seemsoonhotel.com', 'http://www.seemsoonhotel.com', 'October-23-2012-11-39-am-IMG_2475-(120516)---Copy.JPG', 0, 6106),
