(332, 'The Banjaran Hostprings Retreat', 'The Banjaran Hotsprings Retreat is an integrated luxury wellness and spa resort in Tambun, 15 minutes from the city of Ipoh. The 5 star retreat situated on a 16.59 acre valley fringing a cluster of towering limestone hills and features an amalgamation of natural caves, pristine jungle, waterfalls and geothermal hot springs. Combined, it is a self-contained sanctuary consisting of 25 luxury villas offering holistic wellness and spa experiences, unequalled hospitality and distinctive Asian grace. The Banjaran Hotsprings Retreat is a group of Sunway International Hotels & Resorts.', 31, 'No 1, Persiaran Lagun Sunway 3, 31150 Ipoh Perak', '052107780', 'hr.kl@thebanjaran.com', 'www.thebanjaran.com', 'default_employ.png', 0, 6142),
