(336, 'YAYASAN KEMAJUAN ISLAM DARUL RIDZUAN ( KADIR )', 'Kumpulan Dakwah Islamiah Darul Ridzuan (KADIR) ditubuhkan pada 28 November 2009 bersamaan 11 Zulhijjah 1430 di Masjid Sultan Azlan Shah, Jalan Raja Musa Mahadi, Ipoh ,Perak. Kumpulan Dakwah Islamiah Darul Ridzuan ini ditubuhkan bagi memantapkan lagi pergerakan dan organisasi dakwah dan telah disempurnakan oleh ke bawah DYTM Raja Dr. Nazrin Shah Ibni Sultan Azlan Muhibbuddin Shah.\r\n\r\nPada 6 hb Januari 2011 nama Kumpulan Dakwah Islamiah Darul Ridzuan telah di tukar pakai sebagai Pertubuhan Dakwah Islamiah Perak Darul Ridzuan dengan mendapat sokongan penuh daripada Tan Sri Dato'' Seri (Dr) Hj. Harussani bin Hj. Zakaria, Mufti Negeri Perak dan juga Y.Bhg Dato Wan Muhamad bin Dato Shiekh Abd Aziz, Ketua Pengarah JAKIM. Ia telah didaftarkn secara rasminya dengan Pendaftaran Pertubuhan.\r\n\r\nIa kemudiannya dinaiktaraf kepada Yayasan Kebajikan Islam Darul Ridzuan (KADIR) oleh Suruhajaya Pertubuhan Syarikat atas usaha dan anjuran YAB Menteri Besar Peak, Dato'' Seri DiRaja Dr. Zambry Abdul Kadir pada 25 Disember 2011 bersamaan 29 Muharram 1433H.\r\n\r\nKumpulan ini ditubuhkan di peringat negeri Perak supaya kegiatan dakwah dapat dipertingkatkan lagi. Meskipun kegiatan dakwah dapat dijalankan secara rasmi oleh Jab. Agama Islam Negeri Perak, namun terdapat ruang-ruang yang perlu diisi oleh pertubuhan dakwah Islam yang bebas(NGO) supaya kerja dakwah dan syiar Islam diperluaskan lagi di peringkat akar umbi.\r\n\r\n', 122, 'NO 4 & 6, LENGKOK MERU PERMAI 2, HALAMAN MERU PERMAI, BANDAR MERU RAYA 30020 IPOH PERAK DARUL RIDZUAN', '05-2560279 ', '-', 'http://www.kadirperak.com.my', 'November-8-2012-3-03-pm-logo-terbaru-kadir-2012-kecik.png', 0, 6277),
(337, 'PERAK COMMUNITY SPECIALIST HOSPITAL', 'Perak Community Specialist Hospital or PCSH (formerly known as Perak Chinese Maternity Hospital) is an 84 bedded multi-disciplinary specialist hospital and one of the oldest, not-for-profit community hospitals in Malaysia. The Hospital is owned by The Perak Chinese Maternity Association.\r\n\r\nWe are located along Jalan Raja Permaisuri Bainun (Jalan Kampar), a major road in the city of Ipoh. We stand proudly amidst serene surroundings and one can easily forget the hustle bustle of a busy street at our doorstep. This 4-storey hospital has come along way since its humble beginning in 1904 and has a wealth of history behind us.\r\n\r\nOur hospital is served by a team of dedicated specialist doctors and caring personnel. We continually strive to provide comprehensive healthcare supported by modern technologies.\r\n\r\nTogether with the commitment from Top Management, Consultant Specialist and the combined efforts of all Head of Departments and staff, the Hospital successfully acquired the prestigious award of ISO 9001 Certification by SIRIM QAS International Sdn.Bhd on 20th February 2003 and it maintained its certification status to date.\r\n\r\nIn order that there is an infusion of ideas and feedback from all levels of staff within the organisation, operational decisions and mid-term planning are achieved on a consultative basis. Various Committees concerning issues of Quality, Medical Audit, Medical Credentialing, Mortality Assessment, Infection Control, Occupational Safety & health Committee were formed to ensure that we continually improve and maintained its certification status to date.\r\n\r\nIn line with our objective to be a Customer Driven Organisation, we remain responsive to the changing needs of community. We also recognise and respect the individuality of our customers and their needs by tailoring our system and services in the best way possible to meet their requirements.', 29, '277, Jalan Raja Permaisuri Bainun 30250 Ipoh Perak Darul Ridzuan Malaysia', '605-254 559', 'pcsh@streamyx.com', 'www.pcsh.com.my', 'November-8-2012-3-32-pm-PCSH.jpg', 0, 6279),
(338, 'NSL CHEMICALS (M) SDN BHD', 'SL Chemicals (M) Sdn Bhd was incorporated in 1989 and has since grown to be one of the leading and largest lime manufacturers in the region.\r\n\r\nWe operate three (3) state-of-the-art high tech MAERZ Regenerative modern lime kiln plants with a total production capacity of 210,000mt per annum together with roller mills and hydration plants for the processing of downstream products.\r\n\r\nNSL Chemicals (M) Sdn Bhd also owns and operates an integrated quarry, through its subsidiary Kuari Atrah Sdn. Bhd., for mining of limestones for its own lime production as well as sales of aggregates to the domestic market, through its subsidiary Limetreat Trading Sdn. Bhd.	  	\r\nNSL Chemicals (M) Sdn Bhd produces high quality quicklime, quicklime powder and hydrated lime for the local Malaysian market as well as for export markets catering mainly to steel manufacturing, construction, water and waste treatments, pulp and paper manufacturing, mining etc.\r\n\r\nNSL Chemicals (M) Sdn Bhd is subsidiary of NSL Chemicals Ltd, a regional leader in lime and specialized refractory products manufacturing. NSL Chemicals Ltd is a subsidiary of NSL Ltd, a leading industrial group in Asia Pacific which has been listed in the Singapore Exchange since 1964.\r\n ', 37, 'Lot 38046, Mukim Sg. Raia, Batu 5, Jalan Gopeng, 31300 Kg. Kepayang, Perak, Malaysia.', '605-3572351', 'info@nslchemicals.com.my', 'http://www.nslchemicals.com.my', 'November-8-2012-3-37-pm-NSL.jpg', 0, 6282),
(339, 'KAWANG ( Kesatuan Agen-Agen Kewangan Malaysia )', 'Kawang ditubuhkan, dikendalikan dan ditadbir oleh sekumpulan agen-agen yang memasarkan produk-produk kewangan seperti pinjaman peribadi, perniagaan atau perumahan, unit trust, insurans, kad kredit dan sebagainya.\r\nKawang merupakan ''Organisasi Maya'' yang menjaga kepentingan ahli-ahli dari segi keadilan pengagihan komisyen, layanan yang sewajarnya dari organisasi kewangan atau koperasi, kecepatan penyampaian maklumat dan beberapa peranan lain sebagaimana peranan ''Kesatuan Pekerja'' atau Badan Profesional'' di organisasi -organisasi lain.\r\nKawang tidak mempunyai sebarang pejabat urusan, ia hanya dikendalikan melalui pejabat maya iaitu Laman Rasmi Kawang Management iaitu www.kawang.my. Laman web Kawang ini ditadbir dan diuruskan oleh Kawang Management.\r\nKawang tidak mempunyai struktur organisasi sebagaimana persatuan atau kesatuan yang wujud dan dikendalikan oleh golongan tertentu (Lembaga Pengarah atau ahli jawatankuasa). Ini kerana semua ahli dalam Kawang adalah sama taraf. Kawang akan mempunyai ko-ordinator peringkat negeri dan seorang ko-ordinator peringkat Malaysia.\r\nKeahlian  awang terbuka kepada agen-agen sepenuh masa dan separuh masa yang berurusan dengan pemasaran kewangan samada produk-produk kewangan koperasi kredit, bank-bank ataupun institusi-institusi kewangan lain. Pendaftaran keahlian boleh dibuat melalui ko-ordinator negeri atau secara ''online'' melalui pendaftaran online di e-daftar.', 1, 'Ipoh', '013-4282275', 'jamalullail2275@gmail.com', 'http://kawang.my', 'default_employ.png', 0, 6283),
