(342, 'Farmcochem Sdn. Bhd.', 'Established in 1984, Farmcochem is s one of South East Asia''s most dynamic agribusiness companies providing crop proctection and plant nutrition solutions. We are one of the leading companies in the generic crop proctection industry in Malaysia and rapidly expanding our business across the region.\r\n\r\nIn line with our expansion plans in Malaysia, we are looking for outstanding individual to join our dynamic and rapidly growing company. Whether you are an experienced professional or taking that first step in your career, we offer you a unique opportunity to further your prospects and maximize your talent.\r\n\r\nIf you have these qualities, contact us now!', 12, 'No.20-22, Lengkok Rishah 2, Kawasan Perindustrian Silibin, 30100 Ipoh, Perak.', '05-5266601', 'hr@farmcochem.com', 'www.farmcochem.com', 'November-12-2012-12-17-pm-farmcochem1a_02.jpg', 0, 6547),
(343, 'One Global Mobile', 'ONE GLOBAL MOBILE provides the most complete one-stop sales and after-sales service. \r\nONE GLOBAL MOBILE committed to provide users with a rich mobile phone selection of merchandise, convenient way to shop and perfect after-sales service, and is committed to providing consumers with the most complete, highest quality products, most reasonable price and the best mobile phone services.\r\nMoreover, branded and well-known telecommunication companies like MAXIS, CELCOM, DIGI, TUNE TALK AND YES also set up one-stop counter service of Online Bill Payment, Postpaid and Broadband Registration.\r\nFamous brand of mobile phone participated in this mall counters are: SAMSUNG, BLACKBERRY, NOKIA, MOTOROLA, HTC and SONY.\r\n\r\nOther than selling mobile products, there are mobile service centres to diagnose, repair and fix your phone problems: SAMSUNG, SONY, ZTE and Gphone.', 53, 'DGR-11-13, DE GARDEN.NO.1, PERSIARAN MEDAN IPOH, MEDAN IPOH, 31400 IPOH, PERAK ', '05-5423076,', 'oneglobalmobile@gmail.com', 'www.facebook.com/oneglobalmobile', 'November-18-2012-12-56-pm-1-global-mobile-logo.jpg', 0, 6604),
